snippet.title: Maid Cafe at Electric Street -  Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1789030/_/

A leisurely maid cafe adventure set in the electronics district of Nipponbashi, Osaka... made in Shanghai!
Maid Cafe at Electric Street is scheduled to release in 2024.

■ Release Date: 2024
■ MSRP: TBD
■ Developer: Adventurer's Tavern
■ Publisher: PLAYISM
■ Platform: Steam (Windows)
■ Official Page: https://playism.com/game/maid-cafe-at-electric-street/
